lead_paragraph: In years to come when people recall how Leicester's City intrepid Foxes turned sporting logic on its head to become champions of England it will be Jamie's Vardy's rags to riches tale that may sound the most implausible.

headline.print_headline: Vardy's Rags to Riches Rise a Victory for the Dreamers
